Recommends: python3-sentence-transformers,
            python3-torch
Description: Wordlist expansion using semantic similarity for penetration testing
 wl-expand maps seed words to vectors using embedding models (FastText,
 Word2Vec, GloVe) and finds semantically similar words by cosine distance.
 Results can be optionally re-ranked with sentence transformers and expanded
 with lexical mutations (leet-speak, case variants, suffixes, prefixes,
 keyboard typos) modeled after real credential leak patterns.
